{"tid":891670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"性感女球迷球場上任性裸奔 球員全都驚呆了","createTime":"2018-11-06T10:03:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T13:52:01.000Z","uid":205996,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e8d01c840464336b3d099e2aafd8ed66f139af0b","tid":891670,"uid":205996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:03:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-11-06/656/20181106001618.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-11-06%2F656%2F20181106001618.jpg&h=ba2540f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名里積斯堡男孩的女粉絲，竟然一絲不掛全裸衝進球場，替地主隊加油。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yeidcFO5e0g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyeidcFO5e0g&d=CDdQ6ncAsjMY%2BnUCY18RJwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=863106a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yeidcFO5e0g</a><br />\n<br />\n荷蘭丙級足球聯賽本月3日所進行的里積斯堡男孩對上Amsterdamsche FC（AFC）的比賽中，一名性感女球迷突然在比賽過程中，衝進球場中裸奔，甚至翹著屁股湊上球員面前挑釁，讓在場民眾全都看呆了。<br />\n<br />\n根據荷蘭《電訊報》（De Telegraaf）報導，荷蘭丙級足球聯賽如火如荼展開，3日里積斯堡男孩對上AFC，不料比賽中途，一名里積斯堡男孩的女粉絲，竟然一絲不掛全裸衝進球場，替地主隊加油，經過22號後衛提拉瑪（Joel Tillema）身邊時，甚至不惜轉身用屁股頂他，嚇得對方立刻倒退幾步避嫌。<br />\n<br />\n對此，里積斯堡男孩的公關人員亨德里克森（Hendriksen）表示，女粉絲屁股和胸部上大片的黑、黃色塗鴉，並非在草地上滑倒造成，而是以顏料刻意塗抹上里積斯堡男孩隊的代表色；據了解，該名女粉絲也是「Hard Core Rijnsburg Boys」的成員之一。<br />\n<br />\n可惜的是，儘管有女球迷熱情相挺，但里積斯堡男孩最終以2：6不敵AFC，吞下敗仗。"},{"pid":"280aa4ea14990c5b31b4b89025bc19e9952dcea3","tid":891670,"uid":1262,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:03:39.000Z","msg":"望完腳軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943d83627dfda890509f6e9e1f96be556ab41109","tid":891670,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:04:55.000Z","msg":"荷丙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc9bd5b6f05c77571a4dff1482554f6b3e8ba6ac","tid":891670,"uid":3454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:24:11.000Z","msg":"可惜的是，儘管有女球迷熱情相挺，但里積斯堡男孩最終以2：6不敵AFC，吞下敗仗。"},{"pid":"61b0136efb1c02341139ba5e8d8808d15ce14575","tid":891670,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:28:48.000Z","msg":"搞撚錯 咁都輸2:6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4aaa65d36e4d1fabc5866dee2ed68ab8320edf4","tid":891670,"uid":47722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:30:18.000Z","msg":"好大對<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86638847e2add50f2bfced16fd1902a360623ba9","tid":891670,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:30:34.000Z","msg":"好似好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5286885264ec7b71a88bad2a29828d2c868798","tid":891670,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:31:31.000Z","msg":"好大對車頭燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f00d53c26b86a9b97f15a7bb7511ec2b34c047b","tid":891670,"uid":55659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3757b004061ff027dfb16e24656fbd3c4cc0b0d8","tid":891670,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd20d55fe183e75cc1ffda2840f9d502d0676878","tid":891670,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T12:59:18.000Z","msg":"丙組都咁瘋狂"},{"pid":"a87a7c0cc393644b15ae4a28eb1be52b4cf0caae","tid":891670,"uid":121546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:45:47.000Z","msg":"女人裸奔冇人敢攔佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class